#. [race]: id=demon
#: Naia/units/demons.cfg:11
msgid "race^Demon"
msgstr "Demonio"

#. [race]: id=demon
#: Naia/units/demons.cfg:12
msgid "race+female^Demoness"
msgstr "Demonia"

#. [race]: id=demon
#: Naia/units/demons.cfg:13
msgid "race^Demons"
msgstr "Demonios"

#. [race]: id=demon
#: Naia/units/demons.cfg:14
msgid ""
"Legend has it that at the beginning of time, powerful creatures called "
"‘demons’ governed all that existed. The Lords of Light and Darkness, seeing "
"the danger they posed for the balance of nature, banished them to a separate "
"plane of existence, trapped with no means of escape from inside. But time "
"and time again, different versions of the legend have been told by different "
"peoples in different places. Presumably, whatever small amount of truth "
"there was in the original version of the story has since been lost forever.\n"
"\n"
"Either by ignorance, or in an attempt to make sense of the fractured stories "
"gathered from Chaos prisoners, the peoples of Irdya refer more generally to "
"all the vastly heterogeneous races of Inferno by this generic designation. "
"Some go as far as to claim that normal Irdyan creatures may become ‘demonic’ "
"in some form or another, pointing at the Chaos Lorekeepers’ powers and "
"inscrutable nature."
msgstr ""
"La leyenda cuenta que al principio de los tiempos, criaturas poderosas "
"llamadas ‘demonios’ gobernaban todo lo que existía. Los Señores de la Luz y "
"la Oscuridad, al ver el peligro que representaban para el equilibrio de la "
"naturaleza, los desterraron a un plano de existencia separado, atrapados sin "
"medios para escapar desde dentro. Pero una y otra vez, diferentes versiones "
"de la leyenda han sido contadas por distintos pueblos en diferentes lugares. "
"Presumiblemente, la pequeña cantidad de verdad que había en la versión "
"original de la historia se ha perdido para siempre.\n"
"\n"
"Ya sea por ignorancia o en un intento de dar sentido a las historias "
"fragmentadas obtenidas de los prisioneros del Caos, los pueblos de Irdya se "
"refieren de manera más general a todas las razas extremadamente heterogéneas "
"del Infierno con esta designación genérica. Algunos llegan a afirmar que las "
"criaturas normales de Irdya pueden volverse ‘demoníacas’ de alguna forma, "
"señalando los poderes y la naturaleza inescrutable de los Guardianes del "
"Saber del Caos."

#. [unit_type]: id=Demon, race=demon, gender=male,female
#: Naia/units/demons/Fighter_Demon.cfg:5
msgid "Demon"
msgstr "Demonio"

#. [unit_type]: id=Demon, race=demon, gender=male,female
#: Naia/units/demons/Fighter_Demon.cfg:20
msgid ""
"Legend has it that at the beginning of time, powerful creatures called "
"‘demons’ governed all that existed. The Lords of Light and Darkness, seeing "
"the danger they posed for the balance of nature, banished them to a separate "
"plane of existence, trapped with no means of escape from inside. It would "
"take eons before the combined effort of foolish sorcerers and the most "
"dreadful Demon Lord to ever exist would allow Uria unleash her hordes on a "
"ravaged land.\n"
"\n"
"These fighter demons are nimble and sturdy creatures who have largely "
"forgone the need for armor or clothing to protect themselves from physical "
"damage. Although their sharp claws and unnatural strength allow them to tear "
"opponents apart with ease, they usually prefer wielding crude blade weapons "
"to appear even more intimidating in combat."
msgstr ""
"La leyenda cuenta que al principio de los tiempos, criaturas poderosas "
"llamadas ‘demonios’ gobernaban todo lo que existía. Los Señores de la Luz y "
"la Oscuridad, al ver el peligro que representaban para el equilibrio de la "
"naturaleza, los desterraron a un plano de existencia separado, atrapados sin "
"medios de escape desde dentro. Tomaría eones antes de que el esfuerzo "
"combinado de hechiceros insensatos y el Señor Demoníaco más temido que jamás "
"haya existido permitiera a Uria desatar sus hordas sobre una tierra "
"devastada.\n"
"\n"
"Estos demonios luchadores son criaturas ágiles y robustas que en gran medida "
"han renunciado a la necesidad de armaduras o ropa para protegerse del daño "
"físico. Aunque sus garras afiladas y su fuerza antinatural les permiten "
"desgarrar a sus oponentes con facilidad, generalmente prefieren blandir "
"armas de hoja rudimentarias para parecer aún más intimidantes en el combate."

#. [female]: gender=female
#: Naia/units/demons/Fighter_Demon.cfg:107
msgid "female^Demoness"
msgstr "Demonia"

#. [unit_type]: id=Demon Grunt, race=demon, gender=male,female
#: Naia/units/demons/Fighter_Grunt.cfg:5
msgid "Demon Grunt"
msgstr "Soldado demoníaco"

#. [unit_type]: id=Demon Grunt, race=demon, gender=male,female
#: Naia/units/demons/Fighter_Grunt.cfg:25
msgid ""
"The best demon fighters are renowned for their unrivaled strength and "
"performance under any environmental conditions. They obtain and craft new "
"weapons and armor using whatever they can salvage from defeated foes, and "
"learn new combat skills as they adapt to the land to which they are sent by "
"their overlords."
msgstr ""
"Los mejores luchadores demoníacos son renombrados por su fuerza inigualable "
"y su desempeño bajo cualquier condición ambiental. Obtienen y fabrican "
"nuevas armas y armaduras usando lo que puedan rescatar de los enemigos "
"derrotados, y aprenden nuevas habilidades de combate mientras se adaptan al "
"terreno al que son enviados por sus señores."

#. [attack]: type=cold
#: Naia/units/demons/Fighter_Grunt.cfg:39
#: Naia/units/demons/Fighter_Warrior.cfg:41
#: Naia/units/humans/Chaos_Invoker_Lorekeeper.cfg:51
msgid "infernal chill"
msgstr "Frío infernal"

#. [female]: gender=female
#: Naia/units/demons/Fighter_Grunt.cfg:121
msgid "female^Demoness Grunt"
msgstr "Soldado demoníaca"

#. [unit_type]: id=Demon Warrior, race=demon, gender=male,female
#: Naia/units/demons/Fighter_Warrior.cfg:5
msgid "Demon Warrior"
msgstr "Guerrero demoníaco"

#. [unit_type]: id=Demon Warrior, race=demon, gender=male,female
#: Naia/units/demons/Fighter_Warrior.cfg:27
msgid ""
"The few natives of Irdya who have dared underestimate the might of these "
"demonic warriors have invariably suffered horrific deaths at the hands of "
"these blood-thirsty behemoths. The power of the armies of Chaos largely "
"depends on the Lorekeepers’ wisdom in selecting the best fighters to serve "
"them with their undying loyalty to Uria’s cause. But in time, a legendary "
"warrior might rise from the ranks of servility and dethrone a mighty Demon "
"Lord—even their own—and become him or herself a great vassal of Uria."
msgstr ""
"Los pocos nativos de Irdya que se han atrevido a subestimar el poder de "
"estos guerreros demoníacos han sufrido invariablemente muertes horribles a "
"manos de estos colosos sedientos de sangre. El poder de los ejércitos del "
"Caos depende en gran medida de la sabiduría de los Guardianes del Saber para "
"seleccionar a los mejores luchadores que les sirvan con su lealtad "
"inquebrantable a la causa de Uria. Pero con el tiempo, un guerrero "
"legendario podría surgir de las filas de la servidumbre y destronar a un "
"poderoso Señor Demoníaco —incluso al suyo propio— y convertirse él o ella "
"misma en un gran vasallo de Uria."

#. [female]: gender=female
#: Naia/units/demons/Fighter_Warrior.cfg:127
msgid "female^Demoness Warrior"
msgstr "Guerrera demoníaca"

#. [unit_type]: id=Demon Zephyr, race=demon, gender=male,female
#: Naia/units/demons/Fighter_Zephyr.cfg:5
msgid "Demon Zephyr"
msgstr "Céfiro demoníaco"

#. [unit_type]: id=Demon Zephyr, race=demon, gender=male,female
#: Naia/units/demons/Fighter_Zephyr.cfg:23
msgid ""
"Some demons go through a different maturing process and grow large webbed "
"wings, which allow them to use their enormous strength to fly across great "
"distances. As weapons and armor could only hinder them in flight, they must "
"rely on their species’ strong build, long and sharp claws, and their limited "
"control of fire to strike at their prey from above."
msgstr ""
"Algunos demonios pasan por un proceso de maduración diferente y desarrollan "
"grandes alas membranosas, que les permiten usar su enorme fuerza para volar "
"grandes distancias. Como las armas y armaduras solo los obstaculizarían en "
"el vuelo, deben confiar en la fuerte constitución de su especie, garras "
"largas y afiladas, y su control limitado del fuego para atacar a sus presas "
"desde arriba."

#. [female]: gender=female
#: Naia/units/demons/Fighter_Zephyr.cfg:107
msgid "female^Demoness Zephyr"
msgstr "Céfiro demoníaca"

#. [unit_type]: id=Elvish Field Steward, race=elf
#: Naia/units/elves-wood/Border_Field_Steward.cfg:5
msgid "Elvish Field Steward"
msgstr "Intendente de campo elfo"

#. [unit_type]: id=Elvish Field Steward, race=elf
#. [unit_type]: id=Elvish Pathfinder, race=elf
#. [unit_type]: id=Elvish Patrol Captain, race=elf
#. [unit_type]: id=Elvish Wayfarer, race=elf
#: Naia/units/elves-wood/Border_Field_Steward.cfg:20
#: Naia/units/elves-wood/Border_Pathfinder.cfg:20
#: Naia/units/elves-wood/Border_Patrol_Captain.cfg:20
#: Naia/units/elves-wood/Border_Wayfarer.cfg:20
msgid ""
"While the elves of the Valley of Elynia have laws guaranteeing hospitality "
"to visitors from the dunes, hostile invasion attempts are far too frequent "
"for them to afford leaving their borders unguarded.\n"
"\n"
"All members of the Border Patrol have a sworn duty to elvenkind, and from a "
"very young age undergo the most rigorous training. Their diligent study and "
"practice of advanced fight and survival tactics allows them to overcome the "
"natural skills of those born amidst the eternal strife of the desert."
msgstr ""
"Aunque los elfos del Valle de Elynia tienen leyes que garantizan "
"hospitalidad a los visitantes de las dunas, los intentos de invasión hostil "
"son demasiado frecuentes como para permitirse dejar sus fronteras sin "
"vigilancia.\n"
"\n"
"Todos los miembros de la Patrulla Fronteriza tienen un deber jurado hacia el "
"pueblo élfico y, desde muy pequeños, reciben el entrenamiento más riguroso. "
"Su diligente estudio y práctica de tácticas avanzadas de combate y "
"supervivencia les permite superar las habilidades naturales de aquellos "
"nacidos en medio del conflicto eterno del desierto."

#. [attack]: type=blade
#: Naia/units/elves-wood/Border_Field_Steward.cfg:27
#: Naia/units/elves-wood/Border_Pathfinder.cfg:27
